Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Blood Shadow (红莲)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二幕　[闇]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太惨无人道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是南蛮的鬼干的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有那个可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是高手干的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看切口就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,猎鬼的红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在异国狩猎魔物的退魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是让返国的她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加入红莲组织
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,战略补强吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以她的功夫  确实没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本来约定在这里见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她该不会姗姗来迟  说[抱歉  迟到了]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你干嘛那样挖苦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,托你的福  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是猎鬼的红叶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们就是红莲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后你愿意加入我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至今为止我都是独来独往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今后自然无意加入任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且我不喜欢男人当队长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不喜欢受男人那种笨蛋生物指使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,木乃伊女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全身都是绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说遇到她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就会全身被绷带捆起来勒死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好可怕  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？彩乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无精打采的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,任务失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是连带责任！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果早点遇到红叶的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不都是你的错  绕大远路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都怪烈火是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么是我的错？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只好让下一个命令成功才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一个命令已经出来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要调查木乃伊女人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是鬼啦  鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,安士的国威城  有个叫武雷的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像恶魔一样的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:06:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个鬼喜欢抓女人  给城民们带来很大困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武雷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也听说风声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像很难缠的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,似乎是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也有接到要去处理的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然这样  决定明天早上就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这里休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最好小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前去讨伐武雷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都在这里被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同伴之间莫名其妙的起内哄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:06:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请让红莲队的大家  永远和睦相处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小遥真是好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们也要看齐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并没有什么可疑之处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了  既然都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,顺便去求求生意兴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你  小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望可以开全国连锁店  拜托  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肚子痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小茜  你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彩乃  彩乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的名字是赛火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个女人的身体被我接收了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小茜  你快清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小茜  拜托你快清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法  暂时先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神社出现自称赛火的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是这样吗？武雷出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赛火是武雷的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不拿到封灵之镜打倒赛火的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很难接近安士城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,封灵之镜是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你连镜子的事都不知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们情报不足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有封灵之镜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想打倒赛火是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是  那就是先跟保护镜子的众多魔物决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并不容易呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行  我们无法再拖下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我们的同伴被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是  你们这些人太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那个  封灵之镜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她怎么能弄到手？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你  红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有我一个人抢先  有点过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我决定暂时跟你们共同行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的吗？红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法  看你们冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太令人提心吊胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是干什么？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小茜  刚才你居然打我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快把我放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你到底想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小茜  饶了我  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒  还要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒  就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是这个  我等的就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爽得我快融化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小茜  彩乃  你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两个在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两个女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,滚开  臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶的赛火  不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,封灵之镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶的红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我绝不原谅你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好  现在就让你死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打败他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘技  旋风手里剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两个都好威风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们当然不会输给那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是理所当然的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们感情好似变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没指望了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们不久前才祈祷过呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们真是群怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太棒了  是旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我肚子好饿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这旅馆看起来很怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好有品味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是旅馆的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等待各位等到头都大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了  请进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这附近的夜路容易使人迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有的人还走了一整夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来  有六位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位运气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了庆祝今天开店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,饮食费住宿费全免
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是  怎么没看到别的客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然  这里太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家早都睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不提那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明天国威城的武雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们尽量吃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,越看越可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们怎么毫不怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就吃这里的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为很好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对  超级好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看你吃成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也忍不住想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这个变态少装了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶  汗蒙药对你们没效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么快就看破我的秘密计划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,任何人看都会觉得这里可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是  这两人是真的睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她们牺牲自己当诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可怕的红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就让你们看我的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当作给你们的饯别礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是国威城武雷大人的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,努乌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了  告诉我们武雷的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是你们一帮人叠起来  也敌不过的可怕的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们乖乖向我投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是这样  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,国威城的武雷大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,规定每月要献上六个少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不满足他  他就大闹特闹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让牺牲者人数加倍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以大家才不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只好献出少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂  把斗笠拿开  让我看看你们的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然只要要尝你们的人肉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但还是美女比较令人有食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我闻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闻到了男人的可疑味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你替我省了自我介绍的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过然是红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是女性的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道厉害了吧  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看我这招！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,红叶  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勉强还好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像跟大家分散了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就知道男人都是单纯的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:20:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的计划失败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还陷入这种境地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武雷刻意让我们活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这表示
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他想以后再收拾我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那之前嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我赌我们会饿死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到你放弃得这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我等你很久了  大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是天下无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杀死那个男人之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再喝你的人血
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好可怕的怪力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,红莲不过是区区的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,力量就只有这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,红莲的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的死期到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下秘技大往生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你完了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.55,0:22:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是影子术？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还没达成拿下天下的梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是  你这个人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这点程度没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,红叶  你没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烈火  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.44,0:25:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我快射了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.71,0:25:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,射在里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.54,0:25:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有了  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.94,0:25:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烈火  红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.55,0:25:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.75,0:25:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他已经打倒武雷了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.55,0:26:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.02,0:26:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们找到出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.56,0:26:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赶快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.10,0:26:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武雷那家伙已经被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.50,0:26:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是不服从命令的人应得的下场\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.64,0:26:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管那个
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.04,0:26:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剩下的应该没问题了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.04,0:26:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是  已经安排了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.33,0:26:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.20,0:26:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千代丸  晚上在散步吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.61,0:26:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是在哪里检到这个的？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.81,0:26:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.55,0:27:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烈火  晚餐准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.82,0:27:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千代丸  烈火呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.64,0:27:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,月影
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.44,0:27:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烈火  这个送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.71,0:27:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是你与我约定
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.05,0:27:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永远在一起的证物
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.71,0:27:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以搞丢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.52,0:27:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,月影  你还活着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.21,0:27:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.00,0:28:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,**待 续**

